20:00 Wolverhampton Result on Monday 16 February 2026

The 1M 4F 51Y 20:00 JOIN THE MIDNITE MOVEMENT HANDICAP (5) at Wolverhampton was run on Std. It was open to 4yo+ and had a prize fund of 3,716. There were 8 runners. The winning horse was LITTLE MISS INDIA (IRE) who won by hd. LITTLE MISS INDIA (IRE) was ridden by Ashley Lewis. LITTLE MISS INDIA (IRE) had an industry starting price (ISP) of 5/2f.

How the rest of the runners fared:

  • ZENATO (IRE) finished 2nd and was beaten by 0.10 - they had an ISP of 6/1
  • BRODIE'S BOY (FR) finished 3rd and was beaten by 4.10 - they had an ISP of 7/1
  • HACKNEY DIAMONDS finished 4th and was beaten by 5.5 - they had an ISP of 10/3
  • SOLANNA finished 5th and was beaten by 6 - they had an ISP of 5/1
  • ANNANDALE (IRE) finished 6th and was beaten by 6 - they had an ISP of 10/1
  • IT'S A LOVE THING finished 7th and was beaten by 17 - they had an ISP of 8/1
